  <h1>Ἐπιστολὴ εʹ — Περὶ τοῦ ἀκοῦσαι τοὺς λόγους τῶν παλαιῶν</h1>
  <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Fourth letter — About listening to the words of the Ancients</h3>
  <i>May 2021</i>
</div>

<div class="column-center">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="column-2">
      <h2 style="text-align: center;">Introduction</h2>
      <p class="blocktext">In this somewhat more lengthy letter, I talk about various things concerning language and philosophy. It can be understood as somewhat of a ramble, but I thought the subject matter was interesting and decided to write a short letter.</p>
    </div>
